Prerequisites
=============
Before proceding, you have to make sure you have installed and configured
all prerequisite packages.

globus
------
zlib
zlib-devel
----------
libattr
libattr-devel


Building StoRM gridftp-dsi
==========================
Download common

svn checkout --username <username> https://svn.forge.cnaf.infn.it/svn/storm/common/trunk common

Download gridftp-dsi

svn checkout --username <username> https://svn.forge.cnaf.infn.it/svn/storm/gridftp-dsi/branches/gridftp-dsi_1.0.x gridftp-dsi

cd gridftp-dsi

./bootstrap

./configure --prefix=<prefix> --with-storm-gridftp-location=<prefix> --with-globus-nothr-flavor=<flavornothr> --with-globus-thr-flavor=<flavorthr> 

make; make install; make rpm

The other configure options are:

--with-globus-prefix=<globus-location> 
--with-libattr-prefix=<libattr-location> 
--with-libattr-devel-prefix=<libattr-devel-location> 
--with-zlib-prefix=<zlib-location> 
--with-zlib-devel-prefix=<zlib-devel-location>

that you need to specify if they are different by their default values.

For example:

./configure --prefix=/home/joda/tryporting/gridftp-dsi/etics-tmp --with-storm-gridftp-location=/home/joda/tryporting/stage --with-globus-prefix=/home/joda/tryporting/repository/vdt/globus/4.0.7-VDT-1.10.1/sl5_x86_64_gcc412 --with-globus-nothr-flavor=gcc64dbg --with-globus-thr-flavor=gcc64dbgpthr --with-libattr-prefix=/home/joda/tryporting/repository/externals/libattr-devel/2.4.32/sl5_x86_64_gcc412 --with-libattr-devel-prefix=/home/joda/tryporting/repository/externals/libattr-devel/2.4.32/sl5_x86_64_gcc412 --with-zlib-prefix=/home/joda/tryporting/repository/externals/zlib/1.2.3/sl5_x86_64_gcc412 --with-zlib-devel-prefix=/home/joda/tryporting/repository/externals/zlib/1.2.3/sl5_x86_64_gcc412
